OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777911069
OL,3,CSwans turning pink after being fed
OL,4,Cmouldy bread
OL,6,FMel Bloor reports from Caversham
OL,8,FFeeding swans is a traditional family
OL,9,Fpastime, but along the River Thames in
OL,10,FCaversham, wildlife experts say the
OL,11,Fwrong sort of food can seriously
OL,12,Fdamage the birds' health.
OL,14,FAround a third of the flock has
OL,15,Fstarted showing signs of what's called
OL,16,FPink Feather Syndrome, as a result of
OL,17,Fbeing given mouldy bread.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
