FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777911069
OL,3,CSwans turning pink after being fed
OL,4,Cmouldy bread
OL,6,F"Do continue to come down and feed
OL,7,Fthem bread, says Laura. " They're used
OL,8,Fto it. It's a staple of their diet.
OL,10,F"But what we're saying to people is,
OL,11,Fif it isn't good enough for you to
OL,12,Feat, it isn't good enough for them
OL,13,Feither.
OL,15,F"And please dispose of it in the
OL,16,Fproper channels."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
